<p>Assume a knitr (rnw) file with a code chunk </p>  <pre><code>&lt;&lt;function, include=FALSE&gt;&gt;= #' A simple function #' #' @param foo Variable foo. #' @param bar Variable bar.  #' #' @return The product of foo and bar product&lt;-function(foo, bar) {    return(foo*bar) } @ </code></pre>  <p>Now assume that you want to compile the document and in the resulting pdf have the function documentation included in a style similar to an Rd file. Would that be possible?</p>